metadata.name: Temptress Seated
metadata.description:
The temptress readies her bath at La Ferla Manor, fully aware she is being watched.

Featuring Shadia Elise with body paint and cinematography by Roustan (bodypainter.com)

Shot at the home of Dominic La Ferla in Torrance, California.

behind the scenes video available at https://youtu.be/mefgbnETCfc
